item.title: #60 From Stuck to Unstoppable with Todd Jason
item.description:
Most men wake up every day without a clear vision for their future. They’re grinding, they’re hustling, but deep down, they don’t know if they’re actually building the life they want.

If you feel stuck, like you're coasting through life without real direction, this conversation will change the way you think about your future.

I sit down with Todd Jason to break down why clarity is the foundation of success, fulfillment, and freedom - and how you can develop it... Feed: https://app.kajabi.com/podcasts/2147497360/feed

item.title: Ask OTC: Bayern shine without Kane, Marseille's president cries corruption, and how much longer can Luka Modrić keep going?
item.description:
With Harry Kane sidelined, Bayern Munich thrashed Eintracht Frankfurt 4-0—could they actually be better off without him? Meanwhile, Marseille president Pablo Longoria has been hit with a 15-match suspension after accusing officials of corruption, but what’s the full story behind the controversy?


Plus, Freiburg’s Champions League push is flying under the radar, Frank Schmidt battles to keep Heidenheim in the Bundesliga, and just how much more does Luka Modrić have to give before... Feed: https://feeds.acast.com/public/shows/64be9eec0ea5360011fa0255
